  <brief_title>Twenty-Four Hour Combined Multi-Channel Impedance and pH Ambulatory Monitoring: Impedance Reflux Episodes of Patients On and Off Proton Pump Inhibitor Therapy</brief_title>
  <official_title>Twenty-Four Hour Combined Multi-Channel Impedance and pH Ambulatory Monitoring: Impedance Reflux Episodes of Patients On and Off Proton Pump Inhibitor Therapy</official_title>
